# Pytest

- UI tests: `@pytest.mark.asyncio(loop_scope="class")` + `@pytest.mark.usefixtures("browser_context")` when using the shared class browser.
- Use markers: `smoke`, `regression`, `ui`, `api`.
- Allure: `allure.title`, `allure.description`, `allure.step` for reviewer-friendly reports.
- Soft assertions: instantiate `SoftAssert` in `setup_method` and call `assert_all()` in `teardown_method` or explicitly at end of test.
